e is equal to 10 + 1/2 the alchemist‚Äôs level + the alchemist‚Äôs Intelligence modifier.Alchemists can learn new types of bombs as discoveries (see the Discovery ability) as they level up. An alchemist‚Äôs bomb, like an extract, becomes inert if used or carried by anyone else.*¨ (2ü
